-- Eletrobras May Spend Up to $500 Million in U.S. Transmission-Line Company
-- Maria Luiza Rabello
-- 2010-07-29T15:35:19Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-29/eletrobras-may-spend-up-to-500-million-in-u-s-transmission-line-company.html

          
          
             Centrais Eletricas Brasileiras SA
plans to invest as much as $500 million to acquire a stake in a
U.S. transmission-line company, Chief Executive Officer Jose
Antonio Muniz Lopes said.  
 “We will study this year to make a small investment next
year,” Muniz Lopes told reporters today in Brasilia. “Our
focus is to participate in transmission lines.”  
